column2: "Master Gettemhart? He's fighting up ahead. I guess I'm acting as a kind of rear guard."
"When Master Gettemhart is fighting with Darkers, it's best not to get too close."
"By doing so, that person can fight as he pleases with out having to look after others."
"If you have anything to relay to him, you can tell me. But I doubt that's the case."
